graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Reconciler[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller Loop]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Admission]
        RouteRecon[Route Reconciler]
        OAuthRecon[OAuth Reconciler]
        NetPolRecon[NetworkPolicy Reconciler]
        CAMgr[CA Bundle Manager]

        Reconciler -->|creates routes| RouteRecon
        Reconciler -->|manages OAuth| OAuthRecon
        Reconciler -->|creates policies| NetPolRecon
        Reconciler -->|manages certs| CAMgr
        Webhook -->|injects sidecar| OAuthRecon
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|intercepted by| Webhook
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Reconciler

    subgraph "Created Resources (per Notebook)"
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>TLS Edge/Reencrypt]
        Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP]
        SA[ServiceAccount<br/>OAuth]
        Secret[Secret<br/>OAuth Config]
        NetPol[NetworkPolicy<br/>Ingress Control]
        CABundle[ConfigMap<br/>workbench-trusted-ca-bundle]
    end

    Reconciler -->|creates| Route
    Reconciler -->|creates| Service
    OAuthRecon -->|creates| SA
    OAuthRecon -->|creates| Secret
    NetPolRecon -->|creates| NetPol
    CAMgr -->|creates| CABundle

    subgraph "OpenShift Platform"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
        IngressCtrl[OpenShift Ingress Controller]
        ServiceCA[Service CA Operator]
        ImageStreamAPI[ImageStream API]
    end

    Reconciler -->|watches/creates| K8sAPI
    OAuthRecon -->|integrates| OAuthServer
    Route -->|processed by| IngressCtrl
    Service -->|cert provisioned by| ServiceCA
    Webhook -->|resolves images| ImageStreamAPI

    subgraph "Notebook Pod (Created by upstream Kubeflow)"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        NotebookContainer[Jupyter Notebook<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]

        OAuthProxy -->|localhost| NotebookContainer
    end

    Webhook -.->|injects| OAuthProxy
    Route -->|routes to| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer
    CABundle -.->|mounted in| NotebookContainer

    style Reconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthServer fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style IngressCtrl fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style NotebookContainer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
